import React from "react"; import { ExamplePreview } from "components/ExamplePreview"; import * as Section from "components/PageSection"; import previewImg from "./assets/slider.gif"; import { Slider } from "../../../../components/Slider"; export const Task1 = () => ( Task #1 First task! We want you to make a slider. It should look (more or less) like on the gif. You will find all necessary assets in the assets folder in the root of the project.
And remember - do not use any external library for this task. It doesn't have to be identical - but do your best to make it look good!
Place your slider below this paragraph. );
